M||name|good-st-bad-st
M||desc|Craft coherent st through diagnosis of core challenge, guiding policy, and coordinated actions when facing complex problems requiring more than goals and aspirations
M||tags|["st", "st-planning", "problem-solving", "competitive-advantage", "decision-making"]
